            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-792891794" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-792891794" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="792891794">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/deartomato/">[已注销]</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
